# {PKG_FULL} — Paket Kuralları

## Naming (zorunlu prefix'ler)

| Obje Tipi | Prefix | Regex |
|---|---|---|
| Program | `{PKG}_P_*` | `^{PKG}_P_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Include | `{PKG}_I_*` | `^{PKG}_I_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Class | `{PKG}_CL_*` veya `ZCL_{PKG}_*` | `^({PKG}_CL_\|ZCL_{PKG}_)[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Function Group | `{PKG}_FG_*` | `^{PKG}_FG_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Function Module | `{PKG}_FM_*` | `^{PKG}_FM_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| CDS Root View | `{PKG}_C_*` | `^{PKG}_C_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| CDS Interface View | `{PKG}_I_*` | `^{PKG}_I_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| DDL Source | `{PKG}_DDL_*` | `^{PKG}_DDL_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Data Element | `{PKG}_DE_*` veya `{PKG}_DTEL_*` | `^{PKG}_(DE\|DTEL)_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Domain | `{PKG}_DOM_*` | `^{PKG}_DOM_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Structure | `{PKG}_S_*` | `^{PKG}_S_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Table | `{PKG}_T_*` | `^{PKG}_T_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Table Type | `{PKG}_TT_*` | `^{PKG}_TT_[A-Z0-9_]+$` |
| Lock Object | `E{PKG}_*` veya `EZ_{PKG}_*` | (lock obj prefix `E` ile başlar) |
| Message Class | `{PKG}` | tek tablo, paket adıyla aynı |

> Validator: `scripts/validators/check_package_naming.py` bu regex'leri okuyup `cds/`, `classes/`, `programs/`, vb. altındaki dosya adlarını doğrular.

> **Include alt-kuralı — klasik program (std 06 §1 · gate C-INC-NAME-01):** Klasik report/module-pool **tek-body YAZILMAZ**; main = `INCLUDE` + event blokları. Include adı programdan TÜRER: `{PKG}_P_<PRG>` → `{PKG}_I_<PRG>_<Tip><NN>` — Tip: **T**op·**C**ls·**O**=PBO·**I**=PAI·**F**orm·**S**el; NN=01… Örn `{PKG}_P_SIPARIS` → `{PKG}_I_SIPARIS_T01`/`_C01`/`_F01`. Generic `{PKG}_I_TOP` (program-kökü + numaralı suffix yok) YASAK. Include = PROG/I objesi, `programs/includes/`.

